Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:28.37,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}尽管只是平凡的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.37,0:22:34.96,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}却也是连接未来的桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:40.63,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}只要你还留在这世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:43.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}我便总能重整旗鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:49.35,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}伴随着我们的相互思念  迈步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:52.56,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}前路依然漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:55.44,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}但每当仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:59.44,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}那雄伟的彩虹依然在我们眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:04.28,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}一起前进吧  回忆摇曳在云朵之间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:06.95,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}就算遮住了太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:16.42,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1a&HFF&\bord0.3\blur8\c&HD6E6EA&}我也永远相信  光芒就在前方
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------------------IN-----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:52.75,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I wake up tired sick bored and expired
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.21,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I wasn't like this, even had a dream too
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.58,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No one could stop me, bully me, suppress me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:02.55,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終わらない this miserable physical life we're in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:07.93,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とまらない we'll find are way いつも here we pray
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:12.97,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Knockin' on my door and draggin' "real me" out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:28.16,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Break it down, don't ever give up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.24,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now is your only chance to change the stance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:34.45,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Light up! It's your life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.91,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now is the time, fight for your life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.46,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cry not to stop but only to be top
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:43.30,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扉を開け
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.71,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}GO ALL THE WAY OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:07.61,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Climb up high 鼓動を鳴らせ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:12.57,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Break it down, don't ever give up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.45,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now is your only chance to change the stance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:19.00,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Light up! It's your life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.38,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now is the time, fight for your life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.75,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cry not to stop but only to be top
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:27.34,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扉を開け
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.01,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}GO ALL THE WAY OUT!
Comment: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:58.93,IN JP,,0,0,0,,-------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:52.75,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从沉睡中觉醒 伴随着浑身不适
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.21,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我讨厌这种感觉 尽管还做了一场梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.58,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁也不能阻止我 威胁我 抑制我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:02.55,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们这悲惨又现实的生活没有尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:07.93,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们会不止步地寻找前路 殷切祈盼着未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:12.97,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敲响我的心扉 找到真实自我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:28.16,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放手一搏 不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.24,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在是你改变立场的唯一机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:34.45,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃起来吧! 这就是你的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.91,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在是时候了 为你的生命而战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.46,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我咆哮不止 终将登上顶峰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:43.30,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打开那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.71,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全力冲出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:07.61,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}攀登高峰 让心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:12.57,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放手一搏 不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.45,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在是你改变立场的唯一机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:19.00,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃起来吧! 这就是你的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.38,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在是时候了 为你的生命而战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.75,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我咆哮不止 终将登上顶峰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:27.34,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打开那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.01,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全力冲出去!
